title: Reebok Women's Classic Harman Run Sneaker
description: Reebok Women's Classic Leather Harman Run Sneaker elevates your everyday style. This women’s shoe is just the ticket. Designed with a subtle iconic side profile, this shoe carries a strong heritage vibe. You will love the low-cut design for easy, daylong wear. Reebok was founded for one of the best reasons possible: athletes wanted to run faster. So in the 1890s, Joseph William Foster made some of the first known running shoes with spikes in them. By 1895, he was in business making shoes by hand for top runners; and before long his fledgling company, J.W. Foster and Sons, developed an international clientele of distinguished athletes.
